Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends:
 libvulkan1,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends}
Provides: vulkan-icd
Multi-Arch: same
Description: Mesa Vulkan graphics drivers
 Vulkan is a low-overhead 3D graphics and compute API. This package
 includes Vulkan drivers provided by the Mesa project.

